{"tid":1421180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"慈雲山貢茶罷工","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:12:12.000Z","uid":93540,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b513d1dc241c6b863c7d1171d76844c8e2b53c0","tid":1421180,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:16:10.000Z","msg":"話說小弟係呢間貢茶做過一年左右 <br />\n琴日5/8經過既時候見到冇開（周圍幾間鋪都照開）<br />\n呢間係加盟店 老細份人好好 <br />\n對員工幾好 又成日買一大堆零食比我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢都幾緊張盆生意 <br />\n之前生意唔好 睇佢埋數果陣個樣就好想笑鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實呢間貢茶不嬲都係做開街坊生意(係幾條屋邨附近)<br />\n生意都唔會話特別好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以見到佢肯罷工都有啲意外<br />\n既然係同路人 希望多啲黃大仙人/慈雲山撚可以多啲去支持下買杯野飲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xE2Oa61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxE2Oa61.png&h=c67cf34a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"232bb7e546f9603797c38233175ef8bd4b24c2be","tid":1421180,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:16:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"355cd1776fc46b7a9afe774a77fe4c6d5fc94b8e","tid":1421180,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:16:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9ba0d70070253a9ee496987ddec8f6e49ddef002","tid":1421180,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:17:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"a4d1edb62938a952f2b193182e272e9b87c7a27b","tid":1421180,"uid":164523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:17:14.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n支持"},{"pid":"84adb4930ce278c4cf537725a92340583f7a7a92","tid":1421180,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:17:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b5fcf7153b09e090e15dd224d0dda232ed4e1f2e","tid":1421180,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:17:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a2cccc9dd9e170c95930ec7fbf04c95a4567370","tid":1421180,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:18:40.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"6fc1cffc2ba6b6c82477c96c6c73b0c46f39d875","tid":1421180,"uid":205134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:19:41.000Z","msg":"之前有個店員好靚女<br />\n不記好似姓盧"},{"pid":"3c0403fb0131f3565c7bbc385f76ca751bc30ad3","tid":1421180,"uid":59795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:20:53.000Z","msg":"雖然飲過麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過下次行過都買下先"},{"pid":"21411cdfbb496fc49205f6c356cd6ceeb2c98c0a","tid":1421180,"uid":165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3c0403fb0131f3565c7bbc385f76ca751bc30ad3","tid":1421180,"uid":59795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:20:53.000Z","msg":"雖然飲過麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過下次行過都買下先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"貢茶真係⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但今次要支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae8e7bdec808ff6d37b302abc44c62cd3089b17","tid":1421180,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c0403fb0131f3565c7bbc385f76ca751bc30ad3","tid":1421180,"uid":59795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:20:53.000Z","msg":"雖然飲過麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過下次行過都買下先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:26:26.000Z","msg":"相比出面其他分店 其實呢間真係唔差 仲要好乾淨<br />\n所以我自己除左呢間都唔會飲出其他貢茶"},{"pid":"20f8269f5bdc35ee6e5bb4dbdff7137d0f91e4f8","tid":1421180,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d0e32f4a7a81619a2bb2fc61882e4f1c46745edc","tid":1421180,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:33:43.000Z","msg":"因為知道老細既難處 所以見到佢肯罷工先咁意外<br />\n希望大家支持下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d249831f5062aee060e61d4165ad8eff40a8a9","tid":1421180,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"有啲職沖到好撚淡，果次我嗌香芋珍珠奶茶，明顯水多過香芋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71fe237b21294dace4c16f45ac101bcad73940b0","tid":1421180,"uid":89909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:36:54.000Z","msg":"飲埋賞茶啦<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PFSOd8A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPFSOd8A.jpg&h=c95a5055&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d9c9ad4efefc1bad0ee778ac5b1648caebbd9b3","tid":1421180,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:40:45.000Z","msg":"小弟最近亦都番過其他台式飲品店 亦都係加盟店<br />\n612罷工果陣 有人向老細提出不如罷工一日 但老細都唔肯<br />\n睇落好似冇咩野既罷工一日 其實老細付出都好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4edde5ad2675da32a0201227dce2f6e7f828a4af","tid":1421180,"uid":281972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c33e4675dcfe162fc6007bd2cf5cb78028f9200b","tid":1421180,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71fe237b21294dace4c16f45ac1